*2007 - &quot;Onward&quot;
*2008 - &quot;Fun Fun - A Night in Montreal&quot;
*2013 - &quot;Monday Night at the Mensa Disco&quot;
*2016 - &quot;Twelfth of Never&quot;
*2020 - &quot;Augmented Indifference&quot;
*2023 - &quot;The Offspring Project&quot;

