*Felicia R. Lee, &quot;A Leftist Stalwart, Still Fighting the Fight&quot;, &quot;The New York Times&quot;, February 21, 2004.
* Jennifer Schuessler, &quot;A Lion of the Left Wing Celebrates Six Decades&quot;, &quot;The New York Times&quot;, October 27, 2013.

